{"tid":2384392,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"五筒台灣之謎 - 曾志豪","createTime":"2021-01-28T13:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-28T13:54:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a887c08bd93c83ea2e1bf6b3216a73eaba4c66","tid":2384392,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-28T13:54:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210128/2ESH5CBWMJGGJBIAQNAWJMQKMA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210128%2F2ESH5CBWMJGGJBIAQNAWJMQKMA%2F&d=YX1qj72dVL8lCt3J0nVEUvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=49f35afc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210128%2F2ESH5CBWMJGGJBIAQNAWJMQKMA%2F&h=ffe96ad2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210128/2ESH5CBWMJGGJBIAQNAWJMQKMA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n五筒台灣之謎 - 曾志豪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3k22QpoMKL49X9h-H4md67D0wek=/1920x1280/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4Q6AL5PW5RBBDLMRDY4EXNMJ5A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3k22QpoMKL49X9h-H4md67D0wek%3D%2F1920x1280%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4Q6AL5PW5RBBDLMRDY4EXNMJ5A.jpg&h=998328bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那天和朋友聚餐，辯論題目是：「台灣會被五筒嗎？」（武統之謂也）<br />\n<br />\n正方代表陳詞：「早晚會被五筒，因為主上不是凡人，龍顏大怒，隨時動武。而且主上也要向子民炫耀自己功蓋三皇、德超五帝，只有統一江山，才可超越列祖列宗。再加上國際政治混亂、美國內鬥、山中無老虎猴子稱大王，五筒這張牌，是勢必要打的。」<br />\n<br />\n此言一出，有意移民台灣的朋友驚惶失措，放下碗筷，食不下咽。<br />\n<br />\n反方代表哈哈一笑，提出了反對意見。「台灣有秘密武器，可保台海平安。」<br />\n<br />\n友人忙問「是美國的武器嗎？是核彈嗎？是潛艇嗎？」反方代表又笑，「是。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n正方不服氣，「。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n反方搖頭，「美軍當然。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n在場人士開始熱烈討論。「中共會滲透台灣嗎？」「不怕啦，香港人已經用自身的血淚提醒了台灣人啊！」「。。。。。。。。。。」<br />\n<br />\n朋友忽然一聲感嘆：「。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n結論是：五筒？係咩，碰！"}]}